EN: He is wearing glasses with special lenses that can block blue light.

ZH: 这家眼镜店有各种类型的镜片可供选择。
EN: This eyewear store has a variety of lens types to choose from.

ZH: 纯净的镜片可以提供更清晰的视野。
EN: Pure lenses can provide a clearer field of view.

ZH: 请你调整一下镜片，我看不清楚。
EN: Please adjust the lens, I can't see clearly.

ZH: 镜片上有一层抗反射膜，可以减少光线的反射。
EN: The lens has an anti-reflective coating to reduce light reflection.

ZH: 这个品牌的镜片非常轻便和耐用。
EN: The lenses of this brand are very lightweight and durable.

ZH: 深色镜片可以阻挡阳光中的刺眼光线。
EN: Dark lenses can block the glare from sunlight.

ZH: 我想要一副有渐进镜片的眼镜，适合近视和远视。
EN: I would like a pair of glasses with progressive lenses, suitable for both nearsightedness and farsightedness.

ZH: 镜片上有一条小划痕，有点影响视线。
EN: There is a small scratch on the lens, it slightly affects my vision.

